  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK549">
<l>kuṭipuṟaṅ kāttōmpik kuṟṟaṅ kaṭital </l>
<l>vaṭuvaṉṟu vēntaṉ ṟoḻil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In guarding his subjects (against injury from others), and in preserving them himself; to punish crime is not a fault in a king, but a duty.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
